<title>USA: Evergreen Resources offering 2 mln shares.</title>
<headline>Evergreen Resources offering 2 mln shares.</headline>
<dateline>DENVER 1996-10-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Evergreen Resources Inc said Wednesday it was making a public offering of two million shares at $5.75 each.</p>
<p>The offering is managed by Paulson Investment Co Inc and Capital West Securities Inc.</p>
<p>The company said net proceeds of about $10.3 million will be used for the additional development of coalbed methane gas wells on Evergreen's acreage in the Raton Basin of southern Colorado.</p>
<p>After the offering, the company said it will have 9.1 million shares outstanding.</p>
